alaIgmpHelperAddressType.name: alaIgmpHelperAddressType
alaIgmpHelperAddressType.description: Set the address type of the helper address. Must be ipv4(1) and set at the same time as alaIgmpHelperAddress.

alaIgmpHelperAddress.name: alaIgmpHelperAddress
alaIgmpHelperAddress.description: The configured IPv4 helper address. When an IGMP report or leave is received by the device it will remove the IP header and regenerate a new IP header with a destination IP address specified. Use 0.0.0.0 to no longer help an IGMP report to an remote address. Must be set at the same time as alaIgmpHelperAddressType
